posts.subject: FOBS: Yes I'm here edition
posts.body:
FoBS, or Forest of Blue Skin, is a game you already know about and if you're here you probably already have it downloaded. But just in case you haven't, here's all the shit. The password for both is fobs08608

FoBS Side A Ver 1.19 English
https://ux.getuploader.com/fobs3/download/20

FoBS Side B Ver 1.02 English
https://ux.getuploader.com/fobs3/download/19

I lost the pastebin and the original thread wasn't backed up, so I don't have any of the other links. In addition, included images are from the latest news post. There's a few others before this, and if you'd like to take a look at them with a translator, go to http://zell999.blog.fc2.com/
Now the question is if anyone can see this shit. **I feel like dial-up would be faster.**

>>73cb1a6e-8f8d-4974-ad87-ebe9539c590b
I don't understand how these images work. I've put my browser in full screen, and no matter how fast I scroll, it doesn't work. Am I missing something else?

>>49259e53-fa00-4492-8297-75077329193f
I can barely see the illusion with this one. Maybe my eyes just aren't working like they used to. Regardless, thanks friend.
